[normal]Q37 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mr Walker:[bold] Mr Cronin, you spoke earlier about the 
[normal]UK
[normal]’s regulation being a bit of a gold standard.  There is a great debate at the moment around shale and the extraction of that.  What recommendations would you make, or does anything need to change
[normal],
[normal] from your perspective
[normal],
