[normal]Q38 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mr Walker:[bold] We are running out of time, so I appreciate the answers.  There are lots of follow-up questions I would like to be able to ask, but I do not think I will have time today.  I just wanted to pick up on one thing from the Mining on Top submission.  You have said, in order to ensure a healthy future for the extractive industry, 
[normal]t
