[normal]Nigel Jackson: [bold] Good morning, Chairman.  I am Nigel Jackson.  I chair the CBI Minerals Group, and I am also Chief Executive of the Mineral Products Association. 
[normal]Robert Fenton: [bold] I am Robert Fenton.  I am the Secretary of the Mining Association of the 
